---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | RoofingMeter" description="How we handle your data and privacy at RoofingMeter. We're committed to transparency and protecting your information while providing roofing education.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
          <div class="mb-8 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">üè† TL;DR</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We collect minimal data, don't sell your information, and are transparent about everything we do.
              We provide free roofing education and resources‚Äîwe're not a roofing contractor.
            </p>
          </div>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We collect the absolute minimum necessary to provide our services:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                <span><strong>Newsletter Subscriptions:</strong> Email addresses for our free roofing tips newsletter</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                <span><strong>Roofing Calculator Tools:</strong> Anonymous usage data (roof dimensions, material preferences) to improve our tools</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                <span><strong>Contact Forms:</strong> Information you voluntarily submit when requesting contractor referrals or asking questions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                <span><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous website usage data via Google Analytics</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Your information is used solely for:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>Providing free roofing education and resources</li>
              <li>Sending newsletter updates (only if you subscribe)</li>
              <li>Improving our roofing calculators and tools</li>
              <li>Connecting you with pre-screened contractors (with your consent)</li>
              <li>Responding to your roofing-related questions</li>
              <li>Complying with legal obligations (if required)</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We use trusted third-party services with their own privacy policies:
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Google Analytics</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Anonymous traffic analysis</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Email Service</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Newsletter management</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contractor Referral Partners</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Only with your explicit consent</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Web Hosting</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Secure website hosting</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You have control over your data:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your contact information</li>
              <li>Opt-out of analytics tracking</li>
              <li>Contact us to access your data</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent for contractor referrals</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information, but no online service is 100% secure.
              We never ask for sensitive personal information like Social Security numbers, financial details, or exact home addresses through our website.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We use essential cookies for website functionality and analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings,
              but some features like our roofing calculators may not work properly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Roofing-Specific Notes</h2>
            <div class="p-4 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Important:</strong></p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>‚Ä¢ We are an information resource, not a roofing contractor</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ We do not guarantee contractor performance or work quality</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Always verify contractor credentials independently</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ We are not responsible for roofing project outcomes</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ See our <a href="/disclaimer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Roofing Disclaimer</a> for more information</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We may update this privacy policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
              We encourage you to review this policy occasionally.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Have questions about our privacy practices or roofing information?
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="mailto:privacy@roofingmeter.com" 
                 class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors text-center">
                Email Privacy Team
              </a>
              <a href="/contact" 
                 class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors text-center">
                Contact Form
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p>
              <strong>Note:</strong> This privacy policy applies to RoofingMeter.com and our educational content.
              It does not apply to third-party roofing contractors, manufacturers, or services linked from our site.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2">
              A service of RoofingMeter Capital. All roofing information provided for educational purposes only.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
